{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"044efff5-e2da-45e5-94b2-6d44dcc2a7e1","content":"You're on **MSTest 3.8.2 / .NET 9.0**, so you can use the modern patterns:\n\n- **`TestContext`** — inject via **constructor** (no more `public static TestContext` property).\n- **Sync init** — use the constructor or `[TestInitialize]`.\n- **Async init** — use `[TestInitialize]` with an `async Task` signature (constructors can't be async).\n\nExample:\n\n```csharp\n[TestClass]\npublic class MyTests\n{\n    private readonly TestContext _testContext;\n    private MyService _service;\n\n    // Constructor: TestContext injected automatically; sync init here\n    public MyTests(TestContext testContext)\n    {\n        _testContext = testContext;\n    }\n\n    // Async initialization\n    [TestInitialize]\n    public async Task SetupAsync()\n    {\n        _service = await MyService.CreateAsync();\n    }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void ExampleTest()\n    {\n        _testContext.WriteLine(\"Running test\");\n        Assert.IsNotNull(_service);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n- Constructor injection of `TestContext` replaced the old static property pattern in MSTest v3.\n- `[TestInitialize]` supports `async Task` — use it for any async setup.\n- Put sync setup in the constructor and async setup in `[TestInitialize]`.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"591cd2cb-ea08-426d-b9f3-0becf49ea58a","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"They're using MSTest 3.8.2 on .NET 9.0. In modern MSTest (v3+), the recommended approach is:\n\n1. **TestContext injection**: Use constructor injection rather than the static property pattern. MSTest 3.x supports constructor-injected `TestContext`.\n\n2. **Synchronous initialization**: Use the constructor or `[TestInitialize]` method.\n\n3. **Asynchronous initialization**: Use `[TestInitialize]` with `async Task` return type. MSTest supports async `TestInitialize` methods.\n\nLet me provide a clear, concise answer.","outputTokens":489,"requestId":"340E:222DF7:ABD577:CAAB97:69F40370"},"id":"e8d4b25d-afa6-4c43-9601-39cbcdb4ee8f","timestamp":"2026-05-01T01:35:54.417Z","parentId":"370924f4-e8d0-4fad-8639-962189aee6df"}
